## Legendary (downloaded at runtime, not bundled)

  https://github.com/derrod/legendary
  License: GPL-3.0

To surface an Epic Games library as Steam shortcuts, this plugin downloads
the `legendary` CLI from its official GitHub Releases at the user's request
and runs it locally. **`legendary` is not bundled in this repository or its
release artifacts** — the user fetches it directly from the upstream's
distribution, and the GPL-3.0 governs that on-disk binary on the user's
machine, not this plugin's source. This plugin is only an installer + UI +
shortcut writer; its own source is BSD-3-Clause.
